==============================================================================
Industrial IoT OPC UA Data Collector
==============================================================================

This software demonstrates professional Industrial IoT capabilities including:
- OPC UA protocol integration for industrial automation
- Real-time data collection from manufacturing equipment
- PostgreSQL database integration for time-series data storage
- Professional-grade error handling and logging
- Scalable architecture for enterprise deployment

Developed by: Luciano Brido
Contact: bridoluciano@gmail.com
